pageProduct.name: QV Wash Cleansing Bar 100G Twin Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Ego QV Cleansing Bar 100g x 2

- Maintains skin’s natural protective properties and doesn’t strip away natural oils like soap can.

- pH balanced, low-irritant formulation, free from fragrance, colour, lanolin and propylene glycol.

- Soothes ichthyosis, sun-damaged skin, dermatitis, and atopic and infantile eczema.

- Suitable for even the most sensitive skin types.

- Particularly suitable for infants and the elderly.

Ingredients

Cetearyl alcohol and white paraffin.

Methyl hydroxybenzoate.
